90
00:06:12,459 --> 00:06:14,527
And it was a single-parent family.

91
00:06:14,527 --> 00:06:16,459
I grew up with my mother,

92
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:19,927
being chased around by landlords.

93
00:06:22,359 --> 00:06:25,927
So, when I grew up, I set a goal for myself

94
00:06:25,927 --> 00:06:28,760
to build my own house,

95
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:32,225
and to let more ordinary people like us

96
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:34,959
be able to own their own homes.

97
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,927
Congratulations.

98
00:06:36,927 --> 00:06:39,560
It seems your dream has come true.

99
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,927
But I didn't succeed on my first try.

100
00:06:41,927 --> 00:06:43,859
I failed many times,

101
00:06:43,859 --> 00:06:46,760
and it took a lot of experience
to get to where I am now.

102
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:49,225
I remember when I first started out
in the field,

103
00:06:49,225 --> 00:06:50,527
