00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:29,226
I save money to buy designer bags.

275
00:15:29,226 --> 00:15:30,393
You don't like buying bags anyway.

276
00:15:30,393 --> 00:15:33,026
Why are you eating instant noodles?

277
00:15:33,026 --> 00:15:34,226
If I had known,
I would have done the same as you.

278
00:15:34,226 --> 00:15:36,125
I should have spent the money on bags.

279
00:15:36,125 --> 00:15:37,827
At least I could carry them.

280
00:15:37,827 --> 00:15:39,226
Unlike now.

281
00:15:39,226 --> 00:15:40,393
All for nothing.

282
00:15:40,393 --> 00:15:41,794
Now I have to tighten my belt.

283
00:15:41,794 --> 00:15:43,794
What do you mean?

284
00:15:43,794 --> 00:15:45,026
Nothing.

285
00:15:45,026 --> 00:15:48,760
I'm just not destined to have those bags.

286
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:50,325
We have to work our tails off

287
00:15:50,325 --> 00:15:52,260
to buy designer bags.

288
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:54,692
But it's different for Fang Iris.

289
00:15:54,692 --> 00:15:56,026
In just a few days,

290
00:15:56,026 --> 00:15:58,060
she was carrying two different bags.

291
00:15:58,060 --> 00:16:00,593
One of which is only available
through special order.

292
00:16:00,593 --> 00:16:02,159
And the key point is, they were gifts!

293
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:04,827
How nice!

294
00:16:04,827 --> 00:16:06,760
Someone gave her bags that are so hard to get.

295
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,026
Yeah.

296
00:16:08,026 --> 00:16:10,393
I think

297
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,060
she must be a mistress being kept.

298
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:14,893
No way.

299
00:16:14,893 --> 00:16:17,192
She seems to have good taste.

300
00:16:17,192 --> 00:16:19,026
She probably wouldn't like

301
00:16:19,026 --> 00:16:20,460
those balding middle-aged man, right?

302
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:24,125
Who says men who cheat are necessarily bad?

303
00:16:24,125 --> 00:16:27,060
I guess that the balding man
must be quite well-off.

304
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:30,292
Otherwise, how could he have
such good taste in buying bags?

305
00:16:31,292 --> 00:16:33,827
Right.

306
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:37,560
Wait, speaking of it…

307
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:38,560
Don't you think

308
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:41,427
it sounds more and more like Han Xinzheng?

309
00:16:44,526 --> 00:16:46,593
Zhou.

310
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:51,060
Does the VP have a mistress?

311
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:53,359
Mistress?

312
00:16:53,359 --> 00:16:55,260
I…

313
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:57,560
The VP is not that kind of person, alright?

314
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:58,760
Besides, the VP is single right now.

315
00:16:58,760 --> 00:17:01,592
And if he does get a girlfriend,
it wouldn't be a big deal.

316
00:17:01,592 --> 00:17:03,794
The VP has a girlfriend?

317
00:17:03,794 --> 00:17:05,726
- What does she look like? Is she pretty?
- I…

318
00:17:05,726 --> 00:17:06,993
Is she young? Tall?

319
00:17:06,993 --> 00:17:09,325
Is she cute?

320
00:17:09,325 --> 00:17:11,993
Do you really want to know?

321
00:17:12,726 --> 00:17:14,027
I'm not going to say anything.

322
00:17:14,027 --> 00:17:15,293
It's time to get to work.

323
00:17:15,293 --> 00:17:16,426
Zhou.

324
00:17:16,426 --> 00:17:19,527
You're pretty boring.

325
00:17:33,056 --> 00:17:37,197
[A New Message]

326
00:17:40,426 --> 00:17:44,126
[Uncle]
Do you know why cannibals wouldn't eat you?

327
00:17:45,216 --> 00:17:47,325
[A New Message]

328
00:17:47,325 --> 00:17:51,659
[Uncle]
Because your expression is too bitter now.

329
00:17:57,376 --> 00:18:00,336
[A New Message]

330
00:18:01,193 --> 00:18:02,325
[Big Brother]
If possible,

331
00:18:02,325 --> 00:18:04,060
get into the restaurant early.

332
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:06,659
Dad doesn't like people being late.

333
00:18:57,226 --> 00:18:58,893
How about it?

334
00:18:58,893 --> 00:19:00,226
Why do you look

335
00:19:00,226 --> 00:19:02,460
a bit flushed?

336
00:19:03,426 --> 00:19:05,527
Not at all, you're overthinking it.

337
00:19:05,527 --> 00:19:07,159
I can't do this anymore.

338
00:19:07,159 --> 00:19:08,759
Why aren't you dressed
this early in the morning?

339
00:19:08,759 --> 00:19:10,360
What are you, an exhibitionist?

340
00:19:10,360 --> 00:19:12,794
I thought it would be cooler like this.

341
00:19:13,993 --> 00:19:16,527
What are you doing?

342
00:19:16,527 --> 00:19:19,460
The hair dryer is broken,
I thought of borrowing yours.

343
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:21,325
Then why didn't you put on
some clothes before coming out?

344
00:19:21,325 --> 00:19:24,627
Didn't I just say it's cooler this way?

345
00:19:24,627 --> 00:19:25,659
The hair dryer is in the bathroom.

346
00:19:25,659 --> 00:19:27,759
You get it yourself.

347
00:19:35,393 --> 00:19:37,592
Then…

348
00:19:37,592 --> 00:19:38,693
Since you're lending me the hair dryer,

349
00:19:38,693 --> 00:19:40,293
I

350
00:19:40,293 --> 00:19:41,826
will take you to work later.

351
00:19:41,826 --> 00:19:43,759
No need, I want to get to the company earlier.

352
00:19:43,759 --> 00:19:45,159
I don't want to be there just on time.

353
00:19:45,159 --> 00:19:48,159
After you use that hair dryer,

354
00:19:48,159 --> 00:19:49,259
remember to unplug it.

355
00:19:49,259 --> 00:19:50,960
And make sure you close the door for me.

356
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:53,288
Also,

357
00:19:55,259 --> 00:19:57,426
don't be late, okay?

358
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:03,560
I'm closing the door.

359
00:20:05,159 --> 00:20:07,993
- Closing the door now.
- Okay.

360
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:25,993
Morning.

361
00:20:25,993 --> 00:20:29,669
[Business Department]

362
00:20:30,993 --> 00:20:33,759
- Morning, Cindy.
- Morning.

363
00:20:35,092 --> 00:20:36,759
Yingjun, so early?

364
00:20:36,759 --> 00:20:38,460
Came to focus on monitoring the stocks.

365
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:41,000
Okay.

366
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:05,126
What does it matter to me
whether she catches a cold or not?

367
00:21:05,126 --> 00:21:08,126
I'm not her mother, after all.

368
00:21:18,693 --> 00:21:21,393
Superconducting blanket.

369
00:21:21,393 --> 00:21:24,325
Why buy something
if you're not going to use it?

370
00:21:28,426 --> 00:21:31,693
People like you with cold hands and feet,

371
00:21:31,693 --> 00:21:33,092
don't take proper care of themselves.

372
00:21:33,092 --> 00:21:35,226
Seriously.

373
00:21:36,896 --> 00:21:39,938
[Uncle]

374
00:21:50,659 --> 00:21:53,193
That's too nosy.

375
00:21:57,592 --> 00:22:01,527
To think you overworked yourself
to the point of sleeping at the office.

376
00:22:01,527 --> 00:22:02,759
If it's because of the press conference,

377
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:05,659
then why not involve everyone?

378
00:22:24,926 --> 00:22:26,592
Good morning, Chen

379
00:22:26,592 --> 00:22:29,092
Cindy

380
00:22:42,027 --> 00:22:44,360
[Who's the Boss]
Could you help check when you're available

381
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:46,259
that transshipment plan
of our business department.

382
00:22:46,259 --> 00:22:48,159
If anything needs to be modified,

383
00:22:48,159 --> 00:22:49,592
then give me some feedback.

384
00:22:49,592 --> 00:22:51,693
Thank you.

385
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:01,759
Meng Heng, please wait a moment.

386
00:23:01,759 --> 00:23:04,259
Look into my eyes.

387
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:09,259
Stop messing around.

388
00:23:09,259 --> 00:23:11,492
Please take every piece of information

389
00:23:11,492 --> 00:23:14,092
you send out right now seriously.

390
00:23:16,627 --> 00:23:19,092
Take it seriously.

391
00:23:19,659 --> 00:23:21,759
I understand.

392
00:23:26,726 --> 00:23:30,159
Didn't expect Director Zhang's teaching
to be quite useful.

393
00:23:30,759 --> 00:23:32,460
Make them understand

394
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:34,826
that all their efforts

395
00:23:34,826 --> 00:23:38,226
are also paving the way for their own dreams.

396
00:23:40,060 --> 00:23:41,993
Don't you still have
to see Chen about something?

397
00:23:41,993 --> 00:23:43,092
Your approval document
hasn't been signed yet, has it?

398
00:23:43,092 --> 00:23:44,193
I'll take care of it.

399
00:23:44,193 --> 00:23:45,426
Don't worry about it.

400
00:23:45,426 --> 00:23:47,360
My document has already been signed.

401
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:50,293
I went to see her in person.

402
00:23:58,893 --> 00:24:00,592
Chen.

403
00:24:00,592 --> 00:24:01,693
Cindy.

404
00:24:01,693 --> 00:24:02,759
Sorry.

405
00:24:02,759 --> 00:24:04,492
My phone has been acting up
these past few days.

406
00:24:04,492 --> 00:24:06,960
It made it difficult for you
to contact me when the approval was ready/

407
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:09,460
I'm really sorry about that.

408
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:12,926
It's okay.

409
00:24:12,926 --> 00:24:14,226
I knew you would be generous,

410
00:24:14,226 --> 00:24:16,293
and wouldn't fuss over it.

411
00:24:16,293 --> 00:24:17,794
But I was thinking

412
00:24:17,794 --> 00:24:19,759
whether we should start

413
00:24:19,759 --> 00:24:20,960
a secretary group.

414
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,426
This way, if there are any
documents or approval forms

415
00:24:22,426 --> 00:24:23,527
with issues,

416
00:24:23,527 --> 00:24:26,560
then you can address them in the group.

417
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:29,126
I've asked Zhou and Secretary Li
from the planning department,

418
00:24:29,126 --> 00:24:30,527
and they both said okay.

419
00:24:30,527 --> 00:24:33,027
What do you think?

420
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:37,193
Recently, I've felt

421
00:24:37,193 --> 00:24:38,492
like I've underestimated

422
00:24:38,492 --> 00:24:40,092
the job of a secretary.

423
00:24:40,092 --> 00:24:42,193
So, in fact, there is a lot

424
00:24:42,193 --> 00:24:44,726
I would like to learn from you seniors.

425
00:24:44,726 --> 00:24:46,193
It isn't too good

426
00:24:46,193 --> 00:24:48,492
for a rookie like me

427
00:24:48,492 --> 00:24:50,259
to constantly making mistakes, is it?

428
00:24:50,259 --> 00:24:52,627
Right?

429
00:24:59,627 --> 00:25:01,759
Okay, then.

430
00:25:06,092 --> 00:25:09,826
Then I'll create a group chat.

431
00:25:10,460 --> 00:25:13,226
Thank you, Chen.

432
00:25:13,926 --> 00:25:16,027
Goodbye.

433
00:25:20,726 --> 00:25:23,293
Truly able to bend and stretch.

434
00:25:23,293 --> 00:25:24,893
Admire.

435
00:25:24,893 --> 00:25:25,993
If we, the salespeople

436
00:25:25,993 --> 00:25:27,926
aren't a bit flexible,

437
00:25:27,926 --> 00:25:30,048
then you can't achieve great things.

438
00:25:30,048 --> 00:25:33,160
[Uncle]

439
00:25:38,527 --> 00:25:41,092
Miss Gao.

440
00:25:41,092 --> 00:25:43,325
Gao Shuangyun.

441
00:25:46,060 --> 00:25:47,560
Is everyone here?

442
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:49,893
Yes.

443
00:25:49,893 --> 00:25:52,492
Do you need to return a call first?

444
00:25:53,027 --> 00:25:54,460
It's alright.

445
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:57,527
Let's start as soon as everyone is here.

446
00:25:57,527 --> 00:26:01,159
Start with the venue arrangement
for the press conference.

447
00:26:01,159 --> 00:26:04,826
The person in charge of the venue layout is…?

448
00:26:04,826 --> 00:26:06,960
Yun, I'm in charge.

449
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,794
The planning department is busy
with another project now.

450
00:26:08,794 --> 00:26:10,794
So, they won't support this event for now.

451
00:26:10,794 --> 00:26:13,193
But we have already contacted
the people from Bosheng.

452
00:26:13,193 --> 00:26:14,926
So, we'll arrive at the site early

453
00:26:14,926 --> 00:26:16,960
to start with the setup.

454
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,993
Okay, very good.

455
00:26:19,744 --> 00:26:20,926
[Jingdu Sustainable Residence in Taoyuan]

456
00:26:20,926 --> 00:26:23,193
Thank you.

457
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:26,592
It's about time.

458
00:26:26,592 --> 00:26:28,293
Everything is ready.

459
00:26:28,293 --> 00:26:29,659
Got it.

460
00:26:29,659 --> 00:26:31,860
- Sorry, please sign in here, thank you.
- Hello.

461
00:26:31,860 --> 00:26:33,659
If you would like to join the lucky draw later,

462
00:26:33,659 --> 00:26:35,759
then you can scan the QR code here.

463
00:26:35,759 --> 00:26:38,027
And this is today's folder and a small gift.

464
00:26:38,027 --> 00:26:39,360
It contains water and drinks.

465
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:41,527
I mean water and some snacks.

466
00:26:41,527 --> 00:26:42,627
What are you talking about?

467
00:26:42,627 --> 00:26:43,759
Please sign in here, thank you.

468
00:26:43,759 --> 00:26:45,060
Editor Liao.

469
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,193
Long time no see.

470
00:26:46,193 --> 00:26:47,092
- Let me introduce you.
- Hello.

471
00:26:47,092 --> 00:26:48,926
This is Director Zhang from Bosheng.

472
00:26:48,926 --> 00:26:50,193
Here's my business card.

473
00:26:50,193 --> 00:26:52,659
Hello, I'm Zhang Shiping.

474
00:26:55,659 --> 00:26:57,393
Okay, that's basically it
for our press conference.

475
00:26:57,393 --> 00:26:59,259
We'll follow this procedure for the event.

476
00:26:59,259 --> 00:27:02,325
- After that, it's time for the lucky draw.
- Okay.

477
00:27:02,325 --> 00:27:03,693
Yingjun, is the short video okay?

478
00:27:03,693 --> 00:27:05,259
- No problem.
- Good, okay.

479
00:27:05,259 --> 00:27:06,464
Come on.

480
00:27:06,464 --> 00:27:07,659
Hello, everyone.

481
00:27:07,659 --> 00:27:09,126
Hello, please take a seat inside.

482
00:27:09,126 --> 00:27:11,993
Please be careful going up the stairs.

483
00:27:11,993 --> 00:27:15,360
Very good, everyone take charge
of your own tasks.

484
00:27:16,393 --> 00:27:17,527
Miss Gao.

485
00:27:17,527 --> 00:27:18,560
The VIPs and media have all arrived.

486
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:19,592
We can begin now.

487
00:27:19,592 --> 00:27:21,226
Okay, get ready to start the press conference.

488
00:27:21,226 --> 00:27:22,726
This is bad.

489
00:27:22,726 --> 00:27:24,926
The Hope Girl and the mascot
responsible for the opening performance

490
00:27:24,926 --> 00:27:26,426
got into a car accident
because they were rushing to the venue.

491
00:27:26,426 --> 00:27:28,426
How could this happen? Is anyone injured?

492
00:27:28,426 --> 00:27:29,592
There is no life-threatening danger.

493
00:27:29,592 --> 00:27:30,693
But they definitely won't make it.

494
00:27:30,693 --> 00:27:31,960
The opening performance has to be canceled.

495
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,860
We might have to use the introduction video
made by Yingjun

496
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:35,492
as the opening act.

497
00:27:35,492 --> 00:27:37,060
Do we have any other backup plans?

498
00:27:37,060 --> 00:27:39,893
Starting with the video directly is too abrupt.

499
00:27:39,893 --> 00:27:42,659
We'll…

500
00:27:42,659 --> 00:27:43,659
Miss Gao.

501
00:27:43,659 --> 00:27:47,092
I have an idea but I'm not sure if it'll work.

502
00:27:50,159 --> 00:27:52,592
Thank you to all the VIPs
and media friends for attending

503
00:27:52,592 --> 00:27:55,293
Bosheng Architecture & Design's

504
00:27:55,293 --> 00:27:56,592
collaboration

505
00:27:56,592 --> 00:27:59,259
for the sustainable housing in Taoyuan.

506
00:27:59,259 --> 00:28:01,426
So, at the beginning of today's event,

507
00:28:01,426 --> 00:28:03,460
I would like to invite all the guests

508
00:28:03,460 --> 00:28:04,659
to welcome our opening act
with the warmest applause.

509
00:28:04,659 --> 00:28:06,325
Welcome our opening performance.

510
00:28:06,325 --> 00:28:09,527
Welcome the Hope Boy!

511
00:28:10,126 --> 00:28:12,492
Go up.

512
00:28:12,492 --> 00:28:15,560
You can do it.

513
00:28:30,159 --> 00:28:32,960
Hope Boy.

514
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,325
Due to a little situation,

515
00:28:34,325 --> 00:28:36,993
the girl has turned into a boy.

516
00:28:43,759 --> 00:28:44,826
This press conference,

517
00:28:44,826 --> 00:28:46,926
Cindy also put a lot of thought into it.

518
00:28:46,926 --> 00:28:49,659
Why haven't I seen her?

519
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:52,293
She's dealing with important work.

520
00:28:52,293 --> 00:28:55,527
Director Zhang, you'll see her in a moment.

521
00:29:08,027 --> 00:29:09,860
Watching the Hope Boy's dance steps,

522
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:12,259
it also symbolizes
this sustainable housing project

523
00:29:12,259 --> 00:29:13,492
is full of hope

524
00:29:13,492 --> 00:29:15,560
and suitable for living in Taoyuan.

525
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:16,794
Human-centric.

526
00:29:16,794 --> 00:29:18,259
With the heart to care for family members.

527
00:29:18,259 --> 00:29:21,460
Giving more vitality to the architecture.

528
00:29:26,693 --> 00:29:29,993
Let's give another round of warm applause

529
00:29:29,993 --> 00:29:31,759
to our Hope Boy.

530
00:29:31,759 --> 00:29:33,293
Thank you.

531
00:29:33,293 --> 00:29:35,624
Thank you.

532
00:29:38,360 --> 00:29:39,460
Following this stage,

533
00:29:39,460 --> 00:29:40,659
we would like to invite

534
00:29:40,659 --> 00:29:41,659
Director Zhang of Bosheng

535
00:29:41,659 --> 00:29:44,060
and Miss Gao from the construction company
to make your way

536
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:45,759
to the front of our model

537
00:29:45,759 --> 00:29:48,226
for the unveiling ceremony.

538
00:29:55,159 --> 00:29:56,193
Alright, when I count

539
00:29:56,193 --> 00:29:57,426
to one, two, three.

540
00:29:57,426 --> 00:30:00,193
Please have the two honored guests
lift the red cloth.

541
00:30:00,193 --> 00:30:01,860
Are you ready?

542
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:05,393
One, two, three!

543
00:30:07,092 --> 00:30:09,926
Wishing the construction company's
sustainable housing in Taoyuan

544
00:30:09,926 --> 00:30:12,659
success in advance.

545
00:30:17,027 --> 00:30:18,860
Next, we invite Director Zhang

546
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:20,060
to come up and say a few words for us.

547
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:22,126
Welcome.

548
00:30:26,426 --> 00:30:28,872
Thank you.

549
00:30:29,426 --> 00:30:30,527
Ladies and gentlemen.

