836
00:43:56,459 --> 00:43:57,660
Take your time eating.

837
00:43:57,660 --> 00:43:59,793
I'm here with you.

838
00:43:59,793 --> 00:44:02,527
Every time I'm lost and helpless,

839
00:44:02,527 --> 00:44:04,827
